{
  "decision_conditions": [
    "<p>The Development hereby permitted must be begun not later than the expiration of three years beginning with the date of this consent.</p><p><br></p><p>\r\nREASON: In order to comply with the provisions of Section 18(a) of the Planning (Listed Buildings and Conservation Areas) Act 1990 as amended.\r\n</p>",
    "&lt;p&gt;No meter boxes, antennas, satellite dishes, soil stacks, soil vent pipes, flues, ductwork or any other pipework shall be fixed to the elevations of the building.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;REASON: To ensure that special regard is paid to protecting the special architectural and historic interest and integrity of the building.&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;All external brick facing shall match that of the existing listed building or listed wall in respect of type, size, colour, face bond, pointing, coursing, jointing, profile and texture, unless otherwise first approved in writing by the Local Planning Authority.&amp;nbsp; The works shall not be carried out otherwise than in accordance with the approved details.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;REASON: To ensure that special regard is paid to protecting the special architectural and historic interest and integrity of the building.&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;All new works, and works of making good to the external retained fabric, shall be finished to match the original work with regard to the methods used and to material, colour, texture and profile, and in the case of brickwork, facebond and pointing.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;REASON: To ensure that special regard is paid to protecting the special architectural and historic interest and integrity of the building.&lt;/p&gt;",
    "<p>The Development hereby permitted shall only be carried out and completed strictly in accordance with the submitted plans hereby approved and any subsequent approval of details.\r\n</p><p><br></p><p>\r\nREASON: To ensure that the development hereby permitted is carried out in full accordance with the plans hereby approved.\r\n</p>"
